descriptionHtml:
This mod will disable fast travel in Skyrim. So now to get around you must walk on foot, use a horse, stagecoach, or if you have the Dawnguard DLC use a ferry. To help make traveling easier use the [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/76297/?]Skyrim More Stagecoaches[/url] mod and have the Dawnguard DLC so you can use the ferries in some cities. If you want the Skyrim Special Edition version go [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrimspecialedition/mods/1003/?]here[/url]. If you play Oblivion also check out my [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/oblivion/mods/33881?]Oblivion Disable Fast Travel[/url] mod.

Requirements
Skyrim

To install just download then extract folder and drag plugin, and bsa into your data folder.
author: LegoManIAm94
